      "rationale": "Validation was performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry, which is the reference device for this COU. Operating conditions span the full COU envelope. Geometric tolerances of the physical test specimen were documented but batch variability was not characterized — this is a known limitation of the validation corpus; edge cases at tolerance extremes were not fully covered."
