      "rationale": "SST k-omega was selected based on superior performance in the impeller passage boundary layer relative to realizable k-epsilon (sensitivity study VR-03). The Giersiepen power-law hemolysis correlation is standard for rotary blood pump CFD and is supported by the validation comparison in VR-01."
