    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required gradation levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are acceptable under MRL 2 scoping. Output comparison criterion is satisfied with maximum NIH deviation of 18% against the 20% threshold. The assessment team concludes that the CFD model has sufficient credibility to support the COU decision regarding worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The package is accepted.",
